comments: Whiteside (POR) makes marginal contact with Ibaka's (TOR) body during his shooting motion that does not affect the play at the basket.
McCaw (TOR) momentary places his arm to Lillard's (POR) front during his drive that does not affect his SQBR.
McCaw (TOR) makes contact to Lillard's (POR) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Lillard's (POR) path.
Whiteside (POR) places his arm to Lowry's (TOR) front during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Whiteside (POR) is late to the spot and delivers leg to leg contact which affects Hollis-Jefferson's (TOR) ability to defend.
Simons (POR) makes marginal contact to Hollis-Jefferson's (TOR) arm after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Whiteside (POR) makes hand on ball contact during Hollis-Jefferson's (TOR) shooting motion and maintains his hand on ball as he returns to the floor. A correct jump ball is whistled.
Whiteside (POR) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact initiated by Lowry (TOR) and makes contact to the ball.
Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) makes some contact with Simons (POR) arm while rebounding.
Ibaka (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Lillard's (POR) path and slightly extends his arms but he is able to move through contact.

comments: McCaw (TOR) is the last player to touch the ball prior to it going out of bounds.
Anunoby (TOR) briefly places his arm against Lillard (POR) prior to the inbound and disengages not affecting his FOM.

Hezonja (POR) maintains a legal guarding position as he contests Lowry's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
